{
  "version": "1.1",
  "_comment": [
    "Busbar catalog for CellPacker.",
    "",
    "A busbar is a busbar — this catalog makes no distinction between parallel",
    "and series connections.  The generation logic picks a busbar based on the",
    "connection geometry; the role (parallel / series) is a pack topology concern.",
    "",
    "Fields:",
    "  id                        unique string key",
    "  name                      human-readable label",
    "  cell_format               display grouping for multi-P strips; null for universal strips",
    "  compatible_diameter_range [min_mm, max_mm] — auto-filter against cell_diameter",
    "  material                  nickel | copper | nickel-plated-copper | aluminium",
    "  form                      strip | perforated | solid-sheet",
    "  p_rating                  how many parallel cells one piece bridges",
    "  width_mm                  physical strip width",
    "  thickness_mm              physical strip thickness",
    "  offset                    true if the strip can bridge non-coplanar terminals",
    "  in_stock                  toggle in the UI to mark strips you have on hand",
    "  custom                    true for user-added entries (may be deleted in UI)",
    "  preview                   SVG path relative to this file (optional, null if absent)",
    "",
    "1P strips have cell_format: null because they fit any cell whose diameter",
    "exceeds the strip width — they are not specific to a cell form-factor.",
    "Multi-P perforated strips have a cell_format because their hole pitch is",
    "designed for a specific cell diameter."
  ],

  "cell_formats": {
    "18650": { "nominal_diameter_mm": 18.6 },
    "21700": { "nominal_diameter_mm": 21.0 },
    "26650": { "nominal_diameter_mm": 26.0 },
    "32650": { "nominal_diameter_mm": 32.0 }
  },

